Maintainer: Mayra Ilbay <mayra.ilbay@espoch.edu.ec>
Description: This package implements a custom continuous probability distribution (champy), including its probability density function and cumulative distribution function. It also provides pseudo-random number generation using the inverse transform method and validates the results through chi-square goodness-of-fit test.
